graph TD
    A[Lead Generation / Inflow] --> B{Initial Scoring & Qualification}

    B -- Qualifies --> C[CRM Lead Creation/Update]
    B -- Doesn't Qualify --> N[Archive / Nurture Pool]

    C --> D{CRM Lead Data Quality Check?}
    D -- No (Missing/Poor Data) --> E[Remediate Lead Data]
    E --> C
    D -- Yes (Good Data) --> F[Assign to Sales]

    F --> G{Discovery & Deep Qualification}
    G -- Not Qualified --> N
    G -- Qualified --> H[CRM Opportunity Creation]

    H --> I{CRM Opp. Data Quality Check?}
    I -- No (Missing/Poor Data) --> J[Remediate Opportunity Data]
    J --> H
    I -- Yes (Good Data) --> K[Sales Pipeline Progression]

    K --> L{Deal Outcome: Won/Lost?}
    L -- Won --> M[Closed Won / Post-Sale Handoff]
    L -- Lost --> O[Closed Lost / Analysis]

    M --> P[CRM Feedback Loop & Process Improvement]
    O --> P

    subgraph CRM Documentation Quality Gates
        D
        E
        I
        J
        P
    end

    style D fill:#ffe0b2,stroke:#ff9800,stroke-width:2px,color:#333
    style E fill:#ffcc80,stroke:#ff9800,stroke-width:2px,color:#333
    style I fill:#ffe0b2,stroke:#ff9800,stroke-width:2px,color:#333
    style J fill:#ffcc80,stroke:#ff9800,stroke-width:2px,color:#333
    style P fill:#c8e6c9,stroke:#4caf50,stroke-width:2px,color:#333